And why did he marry you?

1508
02:08:30,52 --> 02:08:33,867
Because you and your
husband wanted to loot my father!

1509
02:08:34,753 --> 02:08:38,587
My husband was loyal.
When he was dying..

1510
02:08:38,667 --> 02:08:42,306
