right in front of me!

1544
02:10:50,397 --> 02:10:52,570
You had promised your husband.

1545
02:10:52,907 --> 02:10:55,3
Today, your son is promising you.

1546
02:10:55,930 --> 02:10:57,603
I will not let him
sell anything, mother.

1547
02:10:58,674 --> 02:11:00,536
I won't let him
sell anything, mother.

1548
