your proposal, what do I gain?

1672
02:20:46,709 --> 02:20:48,897
At last you speak your mind!

1673
02:20:48,977 --> 02:20:51,457
Yes.. right said.

1674
02:20:51,537 --> 02:20:53,405
The thing is.. excuse me.

